            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Repeat this process for the remaining pizza base[s]</p><p>Tip: Make sure the pizzas don’t overlap on the tray[s] to avoid raw dough!</p><p>Top with the<strong> torn mozzarella</strong>, <strong>truffled mushrooms</strong> and<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, then drizzle the <strong>remaining truffle oil</strong> all over and tear the <strong>basil leaves</strong> (save some for garnish!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until the cheese has melted and the crust has puffed up and browned – this is your <strong>pizza Bianca with truffled mushrooms</strong></p>",
