    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> salad </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p><p>Scatter your<strong> reserved basil leaves</strong> over the<strong> Pizza Bianca with truffled mushrooms</strong> and serve the <strong>balsamic salad</strong> on top or to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
